-mens-basketball</guid><category>Men's Basketball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="MBB Season Opener" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/10/MBB26-27_SeasonOpener_1920x1080.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The West Virginia University men's basketball team will open the 2026-27 season on Monday, Nov. 2 against Niagara at Hope Coliseum.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_system&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/10/MBB26-27_SeasonOpener_1920x1080.jpg" /><media:content url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/10/MBB26-27_SeasonOpener_1920x1080.jpg"><media:title>MBB Season Opener</media:title></media:content><enclosure url="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&amp;image_path=/images/2026/4/10/MBB26-27_SeasonOpener_1920x1080.jpg" length="1" type="image/jpg" /><pubDate>Fri, 10 Apr 2026 10:30:00 EST</pubDate><s:sport_id>4</s:sport_id><s:story_id>58984</s:story_id></item><item><title>Mountaineers Travel to Texas Tech</title><link>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/9/baseball-mountaineers-travel-to-texas-tech</link><guid>https://wvusports.com/news/2026/4/9/baseball-mountaineers-travel-to-texas-tech</guid><category>Baseball</category><description><![CDATA[<img alt="Matchup vs Texas Tech" src="https://admin.wvusports.com/common/controls/image_handler.aspx?thumb_prefix=rp_primary&image_path=/images/2026/4/9/BB26_Matchup_1920x1080_TexasTech.jpg" /><br /><br />MORGANTOWN, W.Va. – The No. 17 West Virginia University baseball team heads to the Lone Star State for the second time this season to take take on Texas Tech for three games. First pitch on Friday is set for 7:30 p.m. ET, Saturday for 3 p.m. ET, and Sunday for 2 p.m. ET.]]></description><media:thumbnail url="https://admin.wv